node.text: I am so excited to share with you our gorgeous antique door from @thebankantiques72! This one of a kind piece of history is over 150 years old and has been completely restored by them. This is made from European pine and stands 8 1/2 feet tall. It is makes an impressive statement in our foyer! If you have antique door dreams,  message @thebankantiques72! •

node.text: Our faux box beams are from @hewnelements. Made from locally sourced white oak, these beams add a rustic timeless feel to our home. I chose the color Buff but you can custom color match to your specifications. The hand hewn distress adds so much character too! Beams: @hewnelements

node.text: Do you want to create a farmhouse bathroom?  Start with @jeffreycourthd tiles! They offers a wide variety of styles, stones, ceramics and  porcelain tiles. I used 3x6 basalt tile on the wall and floor and the shower is Dream Hex. I love how everything turned out! Read more about @jeffreycourthd on my blog link above👆🏻

node.text:
Experience clean, chilled filtered water at your finger tips. The @elkay_usa EZH2O Liv water filter dispenser is designed to be installed seamlessly anywhere in your home.

The dispenser is extremely stylish and sleek with glass and stainless steel finish. It is also sensor activated for hands free filling. The drip tray will capture any spillage for no mess.

It features a counter that our kids love to view and see how many plastic bottles we have saved. Less plastic helps the environment.

The Elkay ezH20 is the coolest home feature we have in our home. If you are building or remodeling, consider this convenience and money saving appliance! @elkay_usa

node.text: We absolutely love our @shelfology Aksel floating shelves! I chose a natural walnut which blends perfectly with our floors. They were so easy to install with their custom wall bracket. I styled the shelves with art, books, recycled glass, lanterns, beads and more! I love the completed look they provide to our family room! Check our @shelfology for all their custom shelving and gorgeous finishes!
